                                            xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Niẓāmī Ganjavī,
                                        </persName> from the conclusion of the
                                            <title>Iskandarnāmah</title>.<lb/>
                                        <desc>Battle scene, with slain soliders at right.</desc><lb/>
                                        <dimensions type="illustration" unit="mm">
                                            <height>223</height>
                                            <width>132</width>
                                        </dimensions>
                                    </item>
                                    <lb/>
                                    <item n="3"><title>Laylà and Majnūn sit together beside by a
